@startuml Enrollment State Machine
left to right direction

[*] --> UNPAID : Select course

UNPAID --> PENDING_GROUP : Payment successful (group course)
UNPAID --> CONFIRMED : Payment successful (individual course)

PENDING_GROUP --> CONFIRMED : Enough learners reached
PENDING_GROUP --> CANCELLED : Not enough learners or learner cancels

CONFIRMED --> LEARNING : Course starts
CONFIRMED --> CANCELLED : Learner cancels

LEARNING --> DONE : All sessions completed

CANCELLED --> [*]
DONE --> [*]

@enduml
